s_list
  include Introduce
  p(class="mt-10 text-xl font-bold") 최근 글들을 확인해보세요 →
  s_list_rep
    article(class="py-5 group")
      a(href="[##_list_rep_link_##]")
        div
          h2(class="text-2xl font-bold group-hover:underline")
            | [##_list_rep_title_text_##]
            span(class="text-base font-normal text-gray-500/50 ml-1") / [##_list_rep_category_##] / [##_list_rep_regdate_##]
          div(class="flex justify-between")
            div(class="mt-1 break-keep w-3/5 max-h-32 line-clamp-5")
              | [##_list_rep_summary_##]
            s_list_rep_thumbnail
              div
                img(src="[##_list_rep_thumbnail_##]" class="w-full h-32 object-cover rounded-md group-hover:brightness-75")
  div(class="flex justify-end mt-10")
    s_paging
      a([##_next_page_##] class="px-2.5 py-2  rounded-md cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-100 [##_no_more_next_##]") 더보기 →



